    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203210/extras/3b79cae065e120caf045fb60e92fdaf9.poster.avif?t=1768789934\" width=624 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203210/extras/3b79cae065e120caf045fb60e92fdaf9.webm?t=1768789934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203210/extras/3b79cae065e120caf045fb60e92fdaf9.mp4?t=1768789934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Burggeist is a real-time action strategy that features the use of height differences and the terrains as part of your tactics.<br>Move around the field, quickly analyze the situation, choose the effective move to create and defend your Tower.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203210/extras/63363aa5e5d9096b78e3ec3c03553d29.poster.avif?t=1768789934\" width=624 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203210/extras/63363aa5e5d9096b78e3ec3c03553d29.webm?t=1768789934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203210/extras/63363aa5e5d9096b78e3ec3c03553d29.mp4?t=1768789934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Years have passed since Lucile had become motionless. Her husband Ignace, a mathematician from Galacia, was in search of the cure but still completely in the dark.<br>One day he caught his stepdaughter Étoile writing to someone and receiving the messages out of nowhere in her notebook.<br>After some back and forth, the &quot;someone&quot; wrote to her, &quot;To free Lucile, you shall build a tower that reaches the heavens.&quot;<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORATION</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203210/extras/4fc2c11524a57121a895a425e3daa0dc.poster.avif?t=1768789934\" width=624 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203210/extras/4fc2c11524a57121a895a425e3daa0dc.webm?t=1768789934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2203210/extras/4fc2c11524a57121a895a425e3daa0dc.mp4?t=1768789934\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A vast no man's land, Aliscans.<br>Players can roam freely around diverse landscapes of Aliscans. Through various encounters and discoveries, you'll get access to a variety of abilities that will further expand your combat strategy.",
